- * numbers. E.g. "0-7", "0-7,16-23"
- *
- * Example files include:
- * - /sys/devices/system/cpu/online
- * - /sys/devices/system/cpu/cpu0/cache/index0/shared_cpu_list
- * - /sys/devices/system/cpu/cpu0/topology/thread_siblings_list.
